91
00:05:14,690 --> 00:05:16,400
Sei. É maconha.

92
00:05:16,608 --> 00:05:18,235
Como sabe?

93
00:05:18,318 --> 00:05:19,486
Tem etiqueta.

94
00:05:21,613 --> 00:05:22,656
Droga.

95
00:05:24,450 --> 00:05:27,828
